review_text:
This is a really great little tablet for the price – yes, you perhaps pay a little more for the form factor, but it packs a lot in. A few random things to note:
- it has Lenovo's AnyPen technology, which means you can use any non-plastic object more than 1mm wide as a stylus, so you don't have to fork out lots of extra £££;
- while the kickstand has four useful positions, it's worth noting that it doesn't work in a portrait orientation, despite some promo shots suggesting that it might
